OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FAn 18-year-old has been sentenced to
OL,8,Fthree years and eleven months in a
OL,9,Fyoung offender institution for terror
OL,10,Foffences after threatening to blow up
OL,11,FStafford College.
OL,13,FJagger Strang had threatened to kill
OL,14,Fclassmates and had a stash of material
OL,15,Fcapable of making explosives.
OL,17,FHe had told other students that he had
OL,18,Fnumerous weapons in September 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
