FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FStaffordshire Police were contacted by
OL,8,Fa safeguarding officer from the
OL,9,Fcollege.
OL,11,FStrang was arrested after it was
OL,12,Freported he had videos of himself
OL,13,Ftorturing cats and he had told people
OL,14,Fat his college that he was carrying
OL,15,Fknives and that he had a plan to blow
OL,16,Fup the college.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FHe had shown a classmate photos of
OL,8,Fhomemade weapons and discussed an
OL,9,Fattack on their college, alongside
OL,10,Fsharing homemade videos of him
OL,11,Flighting substances in his garden and
OL,12,Fkitchen.
OL,14,FDuring a search of the property,
OL,15,Fofficers seized a number of chemicals
OL,16,Falong with homemade gunpowder and
OL,17,Fthermite. A blow pipe was also
OL,18,Frecovered.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FStrang had pleaded guilty to seven
OL,8,Foffences, including possessing
OL,9,Fexplosive substances, terrorism-
OL,10,Frelated material, and making threats
OL,11,Fto kill at an earlier hearing on May
OL,12,F6th at Leicester Crown Court.
OL,14,FThe teenager was sentenced on Monday,
OL,15,FJune 29th, at Birmingham Crown Court.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
