OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FSearches of his devices found a
OL,8,Fmanifesto, written by Strang in 2025,
OL,9,Fwhich he said, 'I am writing this
OL,10,Fbefore I do something big something
OL,11,Fviolent maybe serial killing maybe a
OL,12,Frampage.' It went on to describe his
OL,13,Fdesire to be like famous serial
OL,14,Fkillers including the Sandy Hook
OL,15,Fschool shooter.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FStrang had told classmates that all he
OL,8,Fneeded to build a bomb was a pressure
OL,9,Fcooker, at this point he had been
OL,10,Ftesting making explosive powders and
OL,11,Fhad the ingredients capable of making
OL,12,Fup to 1.3kg of Thermite and 320g of
OL,13,Fgunpowder.
OL,15,FSearches of the home he was living in
OL,16,Falso revealed a blowpipe which he had
OL,17,Fmade and tested for accuracy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FHis digital devices showed searches
OL,8,Ffor how to make explosives, a 'bingo
OL,9,Fcard' of serial killers he admired and
OL,10,Fmessages describing how he was angry
OL,11,Fwith his life and how he worshipped
OL,12,Fserial killers.
OL,14,FWhile he had a disturbing mindset, it
OL,15,Fwas not submitted to the court that
OL,16,FStrang's actions were motivated or
OL,17,Fconnected to terrorism.
OL,19,FFurther messages showed Strang
OL,20,Fcomparing himself to these killers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FAfter moving from South Africa to the
OL,8,FUK with his parents, Strang is said to
OL,9,Fhave transformed from a 'nice kid' to
OL,10,Fa teenager obsessed with violence.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Dave Rowlands
OL,13,Fsaid: "This was a deeply concerning
OL,14,Fcase involving threats that
OL,15,Funderstandably caused significant
OL,16,Falarm to the students that Strang
OL,17,Ftalked to and staff at the college.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
