OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782848908
OL,3,CTeen, 18, who threatened to kill
OL,4,Cstudents and blow up Stafford college
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,F"Thanks to the vigilance of the
OL,8,Fcollege's students and staff and the
OL,9,Fswift actions of our officers, we were
OL,10,Fable to intervene quickly and prevent
OL,11,Fany potential harm."
OL,13,FWatch the full statement from DI
OL,14,FRowlands:
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@TO]
